
                                                 # User Manual — Fuel & Mileage Tracker






## Introduction

Fuel & Mileage Tracker is an Android application designed to help users manage fuel expenses and calculate vehicle mileage efficiently.

---

## How to Install

1. Download the APK file.
2. Open the APK on your Android device.
3. Allow installation from unknown sources if required.
4. Install the app.

---

## How to Use the Application

### Add Fuel Entry

* Open the app.
* Enter fuel amount, cost, and odometer reading.
* Save the entry.

### View Fuel History

* Open the History section.
* View previous fuel records.

### Mileage Calculation

* The application automatically calculates mileage based on odometer readings and fuel usage.

### Statistics Dashboard

* View fuel expense analysis and mileage statistics.

---

## Features

* Fuel tracking
* Mileage calculation
* Expense management
* Fuel history records
* Statistics dashboard

---

## Troubleshooting

* Ensure the app has required permissions.
* Restart the app if data is not updating properly.
* Reinstall the APK if installation fails.









                                                                                        Privacy Policy



Fuel & Mileage Tracker respects user privacy.

This application does not collect, store, or share personal user information with third parties. All fuel records and mileage data are stored locally on the user’s device for educational and project purposes only.

The application may request certain permissions such as storage access or location access only for application functionality.

No sensitive personal information is collected or transmitted online.

This project is developed for educational purposes as part of a Mobile App Development semester project.







